		  <div style="opacity:0" class="sc-cNKqjZ dPMpmk __pf __pf_NVhUfjnj" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-cHzqoD dSZGnI pf-1_"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="sc-dSfdvi hbFSvJ pf-2_"><div data-section-id="pf-a683" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bSqaIl hxsZTX pf-3_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hkgtus clVJp"><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-4_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-5_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest eSTvWa pf-6_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-8_">How to Unfold &amp; Prep Your Bumper Cover for Installation</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-acb9" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bSqaIl hxsZTX pf-9_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hkgtus clVJp"><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-10_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-11_"><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-12_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-14_">If you’ve just received your bumper cover, you may be wondering why it’s folded.

Most aftermarket bumper covers come folded to assume a more compact form. Folding our bumper covers allows us to help our customers enjoy savings on shipping costs. Since they’re made of shape-memory plastic, they will unfold into their proper shape once they are warmed up properly.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-d715" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bSqaIl hxsZTX pf-15_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hkgtus clVJp"><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-16_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-17_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest eSTvWa pf-18_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-20_">Outdoor Method</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-21_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-22_"><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-23_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-25_">This approach makes use of the natural heat from the sun to restore the bumper cover to its original shape.

It takes much longer but does not require any tools.</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:10px;--line-spacing:26px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-edERGn TYgaU pf-26_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-27_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-29_">Find a spot that gets a lot of direct sunlight (it will need to be in the sun for up to 4 hours).</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-30_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-32_">Open the packaging and remove the bumper cover.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-33_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-35_">Arrange the packaging to lie flat on the ground. This will serve as a clean surface for your bumper cover.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-36_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-38_">Place the bumper cover on the surface in the position facing you.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-39_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-41_">Let the bumper cover sit in the sunlight for three hours.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-42_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-44_">Once you hit the three-hour mark, reposition the bumper cover so that the front part is facing the floor. Leave it in this position for the remaining hour.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-45_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-47_">The unfolded bumper is now ready to be prepped for paint, or installed on the vehicle.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9ace" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bSqaIl hxsZTX pf-48_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hkgtus clVJp"><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-49_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-50_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest eSTvWa pf-51_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-53_">Indoor Method</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-54_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-55_"><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-56_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-58_">If direct sunlight is not available or if you have no outdoor space, you can also unfold the bumper cover indoors using a heat gun.This takes less time but requires more effort and care.</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:10px;--line-spacing:26px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-edERGn TYgaU pf-59_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-60_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-62_">Use the foam packaging as your work surface and place the bumper cover on top.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-63_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-65_">Look for creased areas on the bumper cover. Apply heat to those areas with the a gun.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-66_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-68_">Avoid pointing the heat gun at one spot for too long, as excessive heat can distort or melt the plastic. Keep the gun moving to spread the heat evenly across the surface of the bumper cover.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-69_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-71_">Once the last patch of creased plastic is straightened out, you can consider the bumper cover fully unfolded.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-72_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-73_"><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-jtXEFf WsvLF pf-74_"></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-77_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-78_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest eSTvWa pf-79_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-81_">Reminder:</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-82_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:24px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-83_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-edERGn TYgaU pf-84_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jlsrNB kxxXtk pf-85_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-87_">Take extra care when using a blade or knife to open the packaging to avoid accidentally damaging the surface of your bumper cover.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-7a0a" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bSqaIl hxsZTX pf-91_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hkgtus clVJp"><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-92_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-93_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest eSTvWa pf-94_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-96_">Still need a hand? Call or email us:</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-97_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ lbFEmW pf-98_"><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-99_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-101_">1-888-719-8297</span></p></div></div><d